      "_role": "Computes the consumer's tenant ULID deterministically via SHA256('tenant-name:<repo-org>/<repo-name>') → Crockford base32 (first-char clamp). Invoked by the write-project-entity Step (Mint phase) to populate belongs_to_tenant on the Project entity. The ULID is pre-canonicalised in TDD §Canonical Identifiers — Tool ULIDs (WP-001 reserves the ULID and the schema files at schemas/tools/derive-consumer-tenant-{input,output}.schema.json); WP-002 authors the full Tool entity + Python implementation + fixed test vectors. Cross-WP forward reference is captured here so the Step.tool_ref in write-project-entity resolves at parse time.",
